ince with it. CRA allowed me to quickly get the\nproject started and focus on the design of my components and pages. "), mdx("h2", null, "Technologies"), mdx("p", null, "Bomb finder is build with React with Typescript. It currently isn't connected to\nany backend services so it makes use of the browsers provided features to save\ndata. Currently I am using indexDB (if provided) to save all of the users data.\nI chouse indexdb because it doesn't run on the main thread. If I were to use\nsession or local storage. "), mdx("h2", null, "Deign process"), mdx("p", null, "I'm not a designer but I tried to follow a workflow this project.\nI inital started out this project out by writing my goals for the projects\nand all the pages I wanted."), mdx("h2", null, "Project Status"), mdx("p", null, "This project is at a finished stage. It is mostly completed and is fully\nusable and installable. There are still some small bugs that need to be\nfixed but the initial 1.0 release works. A polish wouldn't hurt it. ed."), mdx("h2", null, "What's Next"), mdx("ul", null, mdx("li", {
